        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Account Management</h3>

        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <button class="faq-question">How do I reset my online banking password?<span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Navigate to Dashboard → Profile → Security Settings → Change Password. You must know your current password to proceed. If you've forgotten it entirely, click "Forgot Password" on the login page. A secure link will be sent to your registered email within 2 minutes.</p>
            <p>You cannot use any of your last 5 passwords, and must meet our minimum complexity requirements (12+ characters, mixed case, numbers, symbols).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <button class="faq-question">What are the daily transfer limits for my account?<span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p><strong>Basic Verified:</strong> $10,000/day internal, $5,000/day external wires<br>
            <strong>Fully Verified:</strong> $50,000/day internal, $25,000/day domestic wires, $10,000/day international<br>
            <strong>Premium (Business):</strong> Up to $500,000/day with dual-authorization setup</p>
            <p>You can request a temporary limit increase through Dashboard → Account Settings → Limit Requests. Approval takes 2–4 business hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <button class="faq-question">My statement isn't showing up — where can I find it?<span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Statements are available in Dashboard → Accounts → Select Account → Statements PDF. Monthly statements are posted by the 5th of each month. We can re-send any statement from the past 7 years.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin-top:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Transfers & Payments</h3>

        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <button class="faq-question">Why is my wire transfer taking longer than expected?<span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Domestic wires typically arrive same-day if submitted before 4:00 PM CT. International wires usually arrive in 1–5 business days depending on the receiving country. Factors causing delays include incomplete beneficiary information, intermediary bank routing, holidays, or enhanced compliance reviews on large amounts ($10,000+).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <button class="faq-question">Can I cancel or reverse a payment I just made?<span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p><strong>Internal transfers:</strong> Can be reversed instantly if within 5 minutes.<br>
            <strong>ACH transactions:</strong> Cancellation requests within 24 hours via Dashboard → Transactions → Cancel ACH.<br>
            <strong>Wires:</strong> Once sent, recall the receiving institution through our fraud team.<br>
            <strong>Bill Pay:</strong> Paper checks stopped via $25 stop-payment order. Electronic payments cancelled within 48 hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin-top:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Security & Fraud</h3>

